OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FAn XL bully savaged an 84-year-old man
OL,7,F"as if he were its prey" which men
OL,8,Fwith weapons could not stop, a court
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FJohn McColl died from his injuries a
OL,12,Fmonth after the attack by the dog,
OL,13,Fcalled Toretto, which had to be shot
OL,14,F10 times by armed police officers who
OL,15,Fwere called to the scene in
OL,16,FWarrington, on 24 February 2025.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
