FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FSean Garner, 31, admits possessing the
OL,7,Fbanned male dog and a female of the
OL,8,Fsame breed without an exemption
OL,9,Fcertificate, but denies being the
OL,10,Fowner of a dog which caused injury
OL,11,Fwhile dangerously out of control.
OL,13,FOn 24 March, a trial at Liverpool
OL,14,FCrown Court heard Mr McColl wandered
OL,15,Fonto the driveway of Garner's property
OL,16,Fin Bardsley Avenue at about 6pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FDavid Birrell, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"After he entered the defendant's
OL,8,Fdriveway, that dog, that XL bully,
OL,9,Fattacked him and it just would not let
OL,10,Fhim go.
OL,12,F"People tried to help him. Grown men,
OL,13,Fwith weapons, hitting the dog. But it
OL,14,Fwas no use.
OL,16,F"The dog guarded him as if he were its
OL,17,Fprey. It savaged him"
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FPolice officers called to the scene
OL,7,Fcould not get to Mr McColl so firearms
OL,8,Fofficers attended and shot the dog
OL,9,Fnine times with a pistol and once with
OL,10,Fa shotgun, the court heard.
OL,12,FMr Birrell said: "That is how much
OL,13,Fammunition was required to neutralise
OL,14,Fthis large, powerful, savage dog."
OL,16,FAn examination of the dog after his
OL,17,Fdeath found no food in its stomach but
OL,18,Fshowed that he had begun to eat Mr
OL,19,FMcColl alive, the court heard.
OL,26,@tD@ROUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FA second dog, called Malibu, was also
OL,7,Fshot by police who "didn't take any
OL,8,Fchances", Mr Birrell said.
OL,10,FThe jury was told Garner avoided
OL,11,Fpolice for two days before handing
OL,12,Fhimself in on February 26.
OL,14,FText messages showed he contacted
OL,15,Ffamily members and "made light of the
OL,16,Fsituation," Mr Birrell said.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@HO]wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FHe said Garner was expected to tell
OL,7,Fthe court the dog was kept securely in
OL,8,Fa tool shed, but the prosecution said
OL,9,Fthat was "a lie" and the dog was kept
OL,10,Fon a patio, with only a metal gate on
OL,11,Fa latch securing it.
OL,13,FMr Birrell said Garner knew the dog,
OL,14,Fwhich he used for breeding, posed a
OL,15,Fthreat to others and in one text
OL,16,Fmessage said it was "missing a few
OL,17,Fnuts and bolts".
OL,19,FHe said the jury would hear expert
OL,20,Fevidence that the dog had not been fed
OL,21,Ffor some time.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@PO]xD@UOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FHe added: "The expert will also tell
OL,7,Fus that the dog appeared to be
OL,8,Fguarding Mr McColl as if he were its
OL,9,Fprey or its food."
OL,11,FThe jury heard Garner kept the female
OL,12,Fdog inside the house, apart from the
OL,13,Fmale, and, according to an expert,
OL,14,Fseparating dogs like that could make
OL,15,Fthem "frustrated and aggressive."
OL,17,FMr Birrell said Garner, now of Belle
OL,18,FVale, Liverpool, was an
OL,19,F"irresponsible" and "reckless" dog
OL,20,Fowner.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@RO]wD@FOUwD@aO]{D@AOU{D@OO]{D@
OL,26,AUOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
