OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774433137
OL,3,CXL Bully attacked pensioner 'as if he
OL,4,Cwere prey'
OL,6,FA jury for the trial was sworn in on
OL,7,FMonday, but was discharged shortly
OL,8,Fafter the case was opened.
OL,10,FJudge Brian Cummings KC said a matter
OL,11,Fhad been drawn to his attention which
OL,12,Fwas "no reflection" on any of the
OL,13,Fjurors.
OL,15,FA new jury was sworn in on Tuesday
OL,16,Fmorning. The trial is expected to last
OL,17,Fbetween five and seven days.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
